{"tid":1384642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞還搞 唔好搞到我ok？","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T03:42:36.000Z","uid":105912,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ff685743d9aa84f26b2c22997ad31439501902","tid":1384642,"uid":105912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:28:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你係咁諗嘅 我屌曬你地全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你班人正仆街<br />\n根本政治同民生就係切肉不離<br />\n你都仲可以覺得依家發生緊嘅事唔關自己事<br />\n塞兩塞就係到屌人哋搞到你<br />\n<br />\n根本所有香港人都有責任去保護香港<br />\n喂你唔幫唔出聲已經理虧 但你話大家唔同立場 ok<br />\n屌你仲講到自己呢件事上好撚慘係受害者！？！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當林鄭硬推送中條例個一刻 所有香港人都已經係受害者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咪撚講到係關心香港嘅市民迫害你搞到你返唔工<br />\n係林鄭條八婆搞到你返唔到工呀！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 爭氣啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65836eec2741861c0d01de774eecb09c101c1cac","tid":1384642,"uid":110851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"去南北極住咪冇人搞到你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"},{"pid":"c6e203e3d22459eeddc38a112f53e4e336ec2a1e","tid":1384642,"uid":105912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw81kU8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw81kU8.png&h=d9ad033b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8986c9f7b7f7bd30bdfd8e96bb3d00ea00ad4fee","tid":1384642,"uid":281584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"琴日陽光咁講<br />\n支共只係要香港人再次係佢SET好嘅箱入面爭取<br />\n利用恐懼、唔想亂、疲累心態、給香港人少少甜頭<br />\n實際係更強烈打壓到香港永不返身<br />\n就好似林鄭嘅天星喜貼街<br />\n支共會休息但不會放棄進逼<br />\nSET底線只係做分化、統戰<br />\n幾十年都係先滅最有力、最威脅嘅敵人<br />\n之後清洗無力和理非<br />\n支共KO國民黨,之後對付支持自己嘅知識分子<br />\n支共真係好驚出老解,香港冧<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地就係支共個春袋條賓周<br />\n用下體控制大腦<br />\n香港人先係莊</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"0d844ad0a896c417d7f5e1e414a4d4dd63f9b5c5","tid":1384642,"uid":211520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n返工仲重要過香港？<br />\n<br />\n85全民大罷工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpbybC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpbybC4.jpg&h=f68a8669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d311bcb10308644b6b5b9d94a2d1dae738aedc04","tid":1384642,"uid":105912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">先生/小姐，我而家跟據警察通例 Police General Orders 第20章 第14條要求你出示委任證，麻煩請你合作。<br />\n如果你無法出示委任證，根據香港法例第228章 第22條，我有合理理由懷疑你干犯假冒公職人員罪。</span>"},{"pid":"88fc1006fd79a4a7158d30b3bc3536be18476896","tid":1384642,"uid":105912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GdFGk5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGdFGk5M.png&h=1d09e265&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"173fbbd8e24a947ca46f5dd25335b3de23aaf369","tid":1384642,"uid":167567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T0